#iOS and Android

These can be found in their respective app stores.

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/artemis-spaceship-bridge-simulator/id578372500?mt=8

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=incandescent.game.artemis&hl=en

Installation is as normal for each platform and the game will work across platforms.

These applications can function as the server or client.

The mobile experience might be best suited to command or engineering.
